--- !u!114 &3565468141906147812
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 9073611175433636603}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: fbeb6d65be27d3b40a131a1e4ace56b5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  steps:
  - message: "Welcome {player}, to the Atlas Research Hangar\u2014your workshop for
      building the first hover vehicle. My name is Gizmo, your companion droid!"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 1
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Hello, Gizmo! What should we do here?
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 1
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: We need to help each other building the hovercraft. First, there's a
      problem in aligning the frame parts. DO you have any idea here?
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 1
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Uhmm, I think there's a problem with the measurements?
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 2
    endTime: 3
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Exactly. Before solving it, you need to know, familiarize and learn
      Units & Measurements, Scientific Notation, and Scalars & Vectors throughout
      this chapter!
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 1
    endTime: 2
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Okay, I would love to learn more, Gizmo!
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 1
    endTime: 2
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: It's nice to know {player}! But first, a quick pre-test will show what
      you already know. Goodluck!
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 2
    endTime: 3
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
